overview.en: SIE is a globally used credit issued by the Star International Blockchain Foundation. The initial SIE is based on the Ethereum erc 20 agreement, and will be transferred to a self-developed public chain SIE chain in the future, to promote the development of whole ecosystems including digital asset trading platforms and other applications (DApps).
overview.zh: SIE是由Star International blockchain 基金会发行的全球通用积分，简称SIE。SIE初期基于以太坊 erc 20协议发行，未来会转移到自研的公有链SIE chain（SIE-chain）之上，推动包括数字资产交易平台及其他应用（DApps）之间的生态体系建设。
